---
title: Open-Faced Tuscan-Spiced Chicken Sandos with Bruschetta-Style Tomato Topping & Scallion Cream Cheese
description: If anything you’re like us, you love a bruschetta appetizer and you also love scallion cream cheese on your morning bagel (we totally have that in common, right?). Our chefs—always innovating—combined these two faves for a genius lunch idea: toasty bread shmeared with scallion-studded cream cheese, layered with juicy Tuscan-spiced chicken, and finished with a tangy, juicy tomato, scallion, and balsamic topping. It’s time to hop aboard the 10-minute express train to Great Lunch City!
